tano-donizetti/" rel="tag">Gaetano Donizetti</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/lelisir-damore/" rel="tag">L\'elisir d\'amore</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/marco-bussi/" rel="tag">Marco Bussi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/pietro-adaini/" rel="tag">Pietro Adaini</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/sara-cappellini-maggiore/" rel="tag">Sara Cappellini Maggiore</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/teatro-carlo-felice-di-genova/" rel="tag">teatro carlo felice di genova</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Alfonso Antoniozzi, Alvise Casellati, Anna Maria Sarra, Filippo Crivelli, Gaetano Donizetti, L\'elisir d\'amore, Marco Bussi, Opera lirica, Pietro Adaini, Sara Cappellini Maggiore, teatro carlo felice di genova"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/a44c5de07732564a59a988ff766b2ff9" alt="" /> <img src="http://1.gravatar.com/avatar/a44c5de07732564a59a988ff766b2ff9?s=100&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="100" height="100" alt="" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 photo avatar-default" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Luca Baracchini"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/luca-baracchini/">View all articles by Luca Baracchini</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="ht